{
  "texts": [
    "In the case of fantasy novel generation (Table 1, Story 4), a complicated imaginary world picture and too diverse a range of secondary characters made their description by AI stereotypical and not connected to the real world.",
    "Describing Element Guardians and their role in the novel, ChatGPT only provided us with such information as \"safe balance\" and \"protect harmony\", depending on which element the guardians are responsible for.",
    "It appears the imaginary world is not well constructed, which is important in the fantasy genre.",
    "We presume that for the best development of the fantasy plot, it is necessary to introduce human ideas into the chat through prompts, as well as carefully analyze each plot twist and character.",
    "This is tiring and requires a lot of time, but it is due to the specificity of the genre."
  ]
}